Each screen translates those events differently.

Screen mode	Button 1	Button 2	Button 3
Menu	     Select	       Up	      Down
Value editor Confirm	    +	        −
Editor hold	Cancel/Back	  Fast +	 Fast −
Practice	 Exit	      Clear	     Speed
Trainer	     Exit	       Dit	      Dah

